column2: select  g.psfMag_u, g.psfMag_g, g.psfMag_u-g.psfMag_g as color, count(g.psfMag_u), m.logMass from galaxy g join SpecObj s on s.bestObjID=g.objId join stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust m on m.specObjID=s.specObjID where g.psfMag_u-g.psfMag_g between # and # m.logMass># order by color desc
